entries.femaleVariant: Ain't easy findin' nova virtus these days... Know what I got last week?
Choom, you won't believe what I had...
Scroll of some pasty white boy from the Revere Courier Complaints Department... Twelve fuckin' hours of my life – wasted.
Complaints department, huh? Yeah, sounds like an XBD, all right.
I was a cow, trippin' on some serious psychedelic shit, and then... they were takin' me to get slaughtered.
Yo, you ever wonder who comes up with this shit?
Some real messed up shit. Had to disconnect after, like, two minutes.
